{"data":[{"date":"13:52 06/07","title":"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, hai chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i \u00e1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 l\u00e1 th\u0103m d\u1ec5 d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1edfi trong b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Zing.vn:\u00a0\u201cU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u01a1 m\u00e0. Vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 ai? \u1ede b\u1ea3ng \u1ea5y, m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9 sao kh\u00f4ng?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 U23, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n k\u00e9m nhau nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ta ph\u1ea3i hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Theo t\u00f4i, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean l\u00e0m c\u00e1c em \u1ea5y lung lay ho\u1eb7c m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin. \u0110\u1eebng suy ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, n\u00ean khen ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c em \u1ea5y v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. M\u1ed9t, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh qua gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Hai, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang ta\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0a ra quan \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u00f4ng Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i chia s\u1ebb: \u201cU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, BHL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m sao ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Pakistan, Nepal. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 thu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1ng k\u00e9m ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\u201d.\u00a0<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-183020.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-183020.html\">V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 Asiad 2018?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Jordan v\u1eeba qua ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Asiad 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c danh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 VN nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n,\u2026 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23. HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng n\u00f3i: \u201cNgo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi, ngay sau khi v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh do VFF \u0111\u1ee9ng ra t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi l\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Australia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018-292-190436.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018-292-190436.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\">Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh: M\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</span><br>\r\n\u0110i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/lo-dien-ke-hoach-bat-ngo-cua-dt-thai-lan-tai-asiad-2018-292-185380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/1/lo-dien-ke-hoach-bat-ngo-cua-dt-thai-lan-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/lo-dien-ke-hoach-bat-ngo-cua-dt-thai-lan-tai-asiad-2018-292-185380.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nHLV Worrawoot Srimaka ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi lo l\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4019","checkdouble":"190502"},{"date":"14:24 06/07","title":"Sao HAGL nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t V-League trong th\u00e1ng 6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/sao-hagl-nhan-giai-thuong-ban-thang-dep-nhat-vleague-trong-thang-6.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VPF trao gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 6 sau pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13 V-League.</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">MinH</span>&nbsp;V\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 6</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh Vuong ghi ban tran Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/thay-gi-sau-tran-thang-nhoc-cua-hagl-truoc-sai-gon-fc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 6 sau pha s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 90,3% s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 6 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3ng Nam tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13 V-League 2018.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. B\u00f3ng \u0111i xo\u00e1y v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eadp tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang r\u1ed3i \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 4 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf V.League 2018, gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha n\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n 30m so v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng. N\u00f3 gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 5 V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 6, Ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh&nbsp;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\">V.League </span>c\u0169ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC l\u00e0 CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Quang H\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-vong-17-vleague-ha-noi-tien-sat-ngoi-vuong-hagl-chia-diem-dang-tiec-168-190182.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/du-am-vong-17-vleague-ha-noi-tien-sat-ngoi-vuong-hagl-chia-diem-dang-tiec.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-vong-17-vleague-ha-noi-tien-sat-ngoi-vuong-hagl-chia-diem-dang-tiec-168-190182.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc</span><br>\r\nCLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay HAGL?</span><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb CLB HAGL thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i V-League. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4018","checkdouble":"190503"},{"date":"15:12 06/07","title":"CLB TP.HCM chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i binh t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ronaldinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/clb-tphcm-chieu-mo-ngoai-binh-tung-la-dong-doi-cu-cua-ronaldinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB TP.HCM v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Marclei Santos.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>CLB TP.HCM chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i binh Marclei Santos</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tan binh Marclei Santos cua TP.HCM tung la dong doi cua Ronaldinho.\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Marclei Santos c\u1ee7a TP.HCM t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Ronaldinho.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/clb-tphcm-chieu-mo-ngoai-binh-tung-la-dong-doi-cu-cua-ronaldinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u00e2n binh Marclei Santos c\u1ee7a TP.HCM t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Ronaldinho.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ebft b\u00e1t v\u1eeba qua, CLB TP.HCM l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i BXH v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u00edt h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u1eabn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Marclei Santos, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Ronaldinho t\u1ea1i Fluminense.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV Toshiya Miura, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan Chonburi. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Thai League 2018, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Marclei Santos t\u1eebng chung chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldinho t\u1ea1i Fluminense. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh ra s\u00e2n 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Marclei Santos l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2017, khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Mitra Kukar, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia Indonesia. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, anh ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 24 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 32 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn TP.HCM, Marclei Santos s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y sau 'l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng' Gonzalo Marronkle v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i binh nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch Hu\u1ef3nh Kesly. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Marclei Santos, CLB TP.HCM s\u1ebd gia t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 9 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh-168-189396.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh-168-189396.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi TP.HCM xu\u1ed1ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\">Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-lai-to-trong-tai-lam-clb-tphcm-mat-diem-168-188337.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-miura-lai-to-trong-tai-lam-clb-tphcm-mat-diem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-lai-to-trong-tai-lam-clb-tphcm-mat-diem-168-188337.html\">HLV Miura l\u1ea1i t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0m CLB TP.HCM m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM, HLV Miura m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4017","checkdouble":"190508"},{"date":"15:40 06/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 0-0 SLNA (H1): \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \"r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda\" \u1edf th\u00e0nh Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/nam-dinh-vs-slna-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs SLNA: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs SLNA S\u00f4ng Lam Ngh\u1ec7 An v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 6/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs SLNA: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs SLNA S\u00f4ng Lam Ngh\u1ec7 An v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 6/7.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/nam-dinh-vs-slna-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190514.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP NAM \u0110\u1ecaNH VS SLNA</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4016","checkdouble":"190514"},{"date":"17:30 06/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 18 V-League: N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, HAGL c\u00f3 th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/truoc-vong-18-vleague-nong-cuoc-dua-tru-hang-hagl-co-them-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi m\u00e0 V-League \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i th\u00ec cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f3ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</h2><h2>N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi SLNA c\u00f3 c\u00fa b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1p ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c b\u1eb1ng chu\u1ed7i 5 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, l\u00fac n\u00e0y cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (17 \u0111i\u1ec3m), S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m) v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM (15 \u0111i\u1ec3m).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang b\u00e1m s\u00e1t nhau nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng c\u00fa v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi th\u1eed th\u00e1ch mang t\u00ean CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 18 V-League N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 18 V-League N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/Truoc-vong-18-V-League-Nong-cuoc-dua-tru-hang,-HAGL-se-co-3-diem-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB TP.HCM c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018, c\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 SLNA, trong khi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y khi ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. S\u00e2n nh\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia t\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>HAGL c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku g\u1eb7p CLB Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n th\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ki\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 cho Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 penalty t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Khanh Hoa vs HAL\" title=\"Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs HAL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/6/truc-tiep-khanh-hoa-vs-hagl-18h00-ngay-65-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0HAGL c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i 'b\u00e1o th\u00f9' sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1ea5m \u1ee9c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m 'b\u00e1o th\u00f9' \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku, HAGL m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 HAGL ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1ed1p 3 tr\u00ean BXH.</p>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 18, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 14 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a 2 v\u00e0 thua 1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111ang b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u00eau h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 19, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t TP.HCM \u0111ang tr\u00ean b\u1edd v\u1ef1c r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. S\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League c\u00f2n di\u1ec5n ra c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 18 V-League\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 18 V-League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Lich-thi-dau-vong-18-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 18 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-nhan-giai-thuong-ban-thang-dep-nhat-vleague-trong-thang-6-168-190503.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/sao-hagl-nhan-giai-thuong-ban-thang-dep-nhat-vleague-trong-thang-6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-nhan-giai-thuong-ban-thang-dep-nhat-vleague-trong-thang-6-168-190503.html\">Sao HAGL nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t V-League trong th\u00e1ng 6</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VPF trao gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 6 sau pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-ninh-vs-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018-372-190090.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tong-hop-quang-ninh-12-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-ninh-vs-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018-372-190090.html\">Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 1-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00e1o th\u00f9</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 Nuti Caf\u00e9 V-League chi\u1ec1u 1/7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4015","checkdouble":"190525"},{"date":"17:33 06/07","title":"5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/6/5-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu CR7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Cristiano Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/5-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-neu-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 hai, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus, t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 ba, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ri\u00eang cho m\u00ecnh, tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Leo Messi. CR7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga trong 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real, trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3 M10 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i c\u00f9ng Barca.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Ronaldo c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu c\u00f9ng Juventus gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Gonzalo Higuain</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng nhau trong 4 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2013. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Karim Benzema v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Napoli.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain se lai nhuong san khau cho Ronaldo\" title=\"Higuain s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u cho Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Higuain s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u cho Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Higuain b\u1eadt kh\u1ecfi Real l\u00e0 b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho Ronaldo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thay v\u00ec l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng cho CR7. Higuain kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng Benzema th\u00ec c\u00f3, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus, Higuain \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed7i khi Juventus chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n sang CR7. N\u1ebfu Higuain ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus, anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Higuain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Mario Mandzukic, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Benzema \u1edf Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Isco v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Isco v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid nh\u01b0 Asensio kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n khi CR7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu n\u1eefa.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco va Asensio co the duoc trao nhieu co hoi hon o mua giai toi\" title=\"Isco v\u00e0 Asensio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/isco.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Isco v\u00e0 Asensio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi Andres Iniesta chia tay T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Isco \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 B\u00f2 t\u00f3t. Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf Real Madrid khi Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi Isco c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Isco \u0111\u1ebfn Real, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span> s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Marco Asensio v\u00e0 Dani Ceballos. V\u1edbi Isco thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Ceballos v\u00e0 Asensio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho ch\u00ednh Isco \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Paulo Dybala</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paulo Dybala l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Palermo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf Juventus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a b\u1edfi Gonzalo Higuain kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kha nang sang tao cua Dybala se duoc phat huy toi da voi su co mat cua Ronaldo\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/dybala.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Dybala \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 18 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Higuain, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDybala ghi t\u1edbi 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Higuain (16). Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i c\u00f2n s\u1ed1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Tottenham</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Real Madrid s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn. Karim Benzema n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i, anh kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real co the mua Harry Kane o He 2018\" title=\"Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua Harry Kane \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/tot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua Harry Kane \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLos Blancos s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Kane duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 135 b\u00e0n sau 187 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Harry Kane th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ef1c cao, Spurs ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Luka Modric cho Real, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn Spurs kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede Real Madrid, hi\u1ebfm khi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Bale t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u00f9ng nhau. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thay v\u00ec ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale se quyet tam chung to minh khi Ronaldo ra di\" title=\"Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi Bale v\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu m\u1edd CR7 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm, b\u1edfi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 Lopetegui \u0111\u1ebfn, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Bale c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 v\u1edbi Isco b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u00f2n Bale ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00e3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Serie A</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">La Liga \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Serie A khi h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao c\u1ee1 b\u1ef1 v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u NHM tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sersie A vui mung khi don mot ngoi sao nhu Ronaldo\" title=\"Sersie A vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/serie-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sersie A vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Serie A kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n sang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ph\u00e1p, Anh hay T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi th\u1ed5i v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u00f3 gi\u00fap Serie A \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sau s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a CR7 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4014","checkdouble":"190526"},{"date":"12:32 06/07","title":"\"Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/chelsea-se-phai-mua-ca-doi-hinh-neu-de-willian-va-hazard-ra-di.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Wayne Bridge cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 hai ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Chelsea c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t Willian v\u00e0 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Willian v\u00e0 Hazard \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Hazard \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Willian c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona li\u00ean h\u1ec7 g\u1eaft gao nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Wayne Bridge, The Blues s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Willian v\u00e0 Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/chelsea-se-phai-mua-ca-doi-hinh-neu-de-willian-va-hazard-ra-di.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bridge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cHai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Willian v\u00e0 Hazard. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Vi\u1ec7c Willian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0 Hazard n\u1ed1i b\u01b0\u1edbc theo sau, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i mua c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay h\u1ecd b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Hazard \u0111ang ngh\u0129 g\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1. Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Hazard mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i th\u00ec li\u1ec7u Chelsea c\u00f3 n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn n\u1eefa hay kh\u00f4ng?\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0i to\u00e1n nan gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/bi-chelsea-duoi-co-conte-mat-luon-noi-nuong-nau-can-toi-doi-hoi-184-187354.html\" target=\"_blank\">t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Conte</span> kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn cho m\u1ecdi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e2m v\u00e0o \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi HLV Maurizio Sarri nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi tranh nh\u01b0ng Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00ec nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed5n ngang ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft ai s\u1ebd l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea. V\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d, Brigde n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang kh\u00e1 m\u01a1 h\u1ed3. V\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng lo n\u1eefa, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ra v\u00e0o n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-gui-loi-de-nghi-thu-2-mua-sao-chelsea-180-190491.html\">Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 mua sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ndombele-thay-kante-172-190438.html\">S\u1ee3 PSG \u201ccu\u1ed7m\u201d Kante, Chelsea nh\u1eafm sao Lyon</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4013","checkdouble":"190498"},{"date":"14:54 06/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! 2 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pep sau khi r\u1eddi Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/30/day-2-ben-do-tiem-nang-cua-pep-sau-khi-roi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pep Guardiola r\u1eddi Man City \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil ho\u1eb7c Argentina, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Metro c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep Guardiola mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110TQG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep Guardiola l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf TBN, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola r\u1eddi Man City D\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil v\u00e0 Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola r\u1eddi Man City D\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil v\u00e0 Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/16/Pep-Guardiola-roi-Man-City-Dan-dat-Brazil-va-Argentina-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110TQG sau khi r\u1eddi Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Barca, Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Man City, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 47 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Pep kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110TQG sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i CLB.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;S\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eady. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0110TQG sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng&nbsp;v\u1edbi Man City, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi CLB, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u1edf Man City&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pep c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil ho\u1eb7c Argentina</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep Guardiola r\u1eddi Man City \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil ho\u1eb7c Argentina, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Metro c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola r\u1eddi Man City D\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil v\u00e0 Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola r\u1eddi Man City D\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil v\u00e0 Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/tuyen-anh-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-nho-pep-guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil ho\u1eb7c Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2021, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man xanh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0110TQG.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Pep \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City th\u00ec v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 18 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2022, HLV \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Pep mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh y\u00eau th\u00edch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam M\u1ef9, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Argentina ho\u1eb7c Brazil.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City, Nicolas Otamendi v\u00e0 Sergio Aguero l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Fernandinho, Ederson v\u00e0 Gabriel Jesus l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f9ng Brazil g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4012","checkdouble":"190504"},{"date":"16:27 06/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Cristian Pavon","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/pavon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00f4ng tin Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Pavon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cristian Pavon l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Boca Juniors. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 26 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Thuc-hu-vu-Arsenal-mua-Cristian-Pavon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Pavon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Pavon l\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u1eadt b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pavon v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pavon</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Fernando Hidalgo c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/pavon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Arsenal ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Pavon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Arsenal. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Boca, Daniel Angelici tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng Pavon s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o, d\u00f9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c hay kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Pavon, vi\u1ec7c gia\u00a0h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch l\u00e2u d\u00e0i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBoca \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef Pavon \u1edf l\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Pavon l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Boca, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4011","checkdouble":"190516"},{"date":"17:00 06/07","title":"Klopp: Karius b\u1ecb sang ch\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua Real Madrid.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKarius v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoris Karius \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i 2 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn Liverpool h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh n\u00e9m b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Karim Benzema khi\u1ebfn The Kop b\u1ecb m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Karius l\u1ea1i b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd thua b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m Melwood \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real c\u00f9ng pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o Sergio Ramos v\u1edbi Karius.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00e2m l\u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e1c s\u0129 g\u1ecdi cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 n\u00f3i: Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng\u201d, Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius. \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111i trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c5 ng\u00e0y sau, Karius v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n h\u1ecfi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 n\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i c\u1edb, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Ramos, 100%.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ecf l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eb1ng sau</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKlopp cho bi\u1ebft Karius v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real sau l\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19. \u201cN\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3 ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 x\u1ea3y ra l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri-172-190490.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-len-tieng-choc-tuc-man-utd-172-190403.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-viec-salah-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-liverpool-172-190179.html\">Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/salah-chinh-thuc-ky-hop-dong-dai-han-voi-liverpool-172-190174.html\">Salah k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4010","checkdouble":"190518"},{"date":"17:55 06/07","title":"Conte nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi Chelsea: \"T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/13/conte-nhan-gui-chelsea-toi-van-co-hop-dong-day-nhe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 coi nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba t\u1ea1i The Blues l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng HLV Antonio Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Chelsea khi cho r\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n cam k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i CLB.\r\n</h2><h2>Conte v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i quy\u1ec1n h\u00e0nh \u1edf Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. Trong l\u00fac c\u00e1c k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea5t b\u1eadt v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i g\u00ec tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, The Blues \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ee5 Antonio Conte. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Conte mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u00f9ng d\u1eb1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Times \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Conte \u0111\u00e3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, khi m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eedi email cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra \u00fd t\u1ebf - Conte \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Chelsea, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00f2i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng\" title=\"Chelsea Conte ava\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/du-am-newcastle-vs-chelsea-phia-truoc-la-dia-nguc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Chelsea, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00f2i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u1eb1ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 Hai tu\u1ea7n sau m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1eafc r\u1ed1i trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 t\u01a1 v\u00f2, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi &ndash; ch\u1ec9 5 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Premier League b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, CLB th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec1n cho Antonio Conte, khi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh th\u00eam chi ph\u00ed cho \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Chelsea, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng c\u00f2n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f2n r\u00fat t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u1eeb CLB. Theo cam k\u1ebft, n\u1ebfu HLV Italia kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, b\u1edfi The Blues \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-se-phai-mua-ca-doi-hinh-neu-de-willian-va-hazard-ra-di-172-190498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/chelsea-se-phai-mua-ca-doi-hinh-neu-de-willian-va-hazard-ra-di.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-se-phai-mua-ca-doi-hinh-neu-de-willian-va-hazard-ra-di-172-190498.html\">Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Wayne Bridge cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 hai ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid-172-190411.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid-172-190411.html\">Chelsea vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t con m\u1ed3i v\u00ec... Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Argentina &ndash; Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4009","checkdouble":"190524"},{"date":"10:01 06/07","title":"Juventus l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/juventus-la-buoc-lui-su-nghiep-cua-ronaldo.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i cho CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u vinh quang n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3, k\u00e9o theo ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus c\u1ea3.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/juventus-la-buoc-lui-su-nghiep-cua-ronaldo.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u00ednh h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i. C\u00e1c CLB \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 Europa League trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u00e1nh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, phong c\u00e1ch Italia s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Ronaldo, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb n\u1eefa. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi Serie A.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus n\u00eau ra l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed3i v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng thuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfm ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Real Madrid sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro (88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4008","checkdouble":"190480"},{"date":"10:26 06/07","title":"Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/messi-muon-barca-mua-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, M10 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Lionel-Messi-muon-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t Griezmann ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, M10 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMessi hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Barca mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Pogba t\u1edbi Camp Nou, anh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Philippe Coutinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 cho Messi \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec Real c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Pogba, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n Pogba, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/bat-chap-mau-thuan-voi-mourinho-pogba-se-o-lai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Paul Pogba cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pogba c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fred. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Pogba s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nh\u1eb1m t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4007","checkdouble":"190483"}]}